The two text files are for old way of adding intent and utterances.  The JSON uses the new SKILL BUILDER where you can import your own JSON file.  Use whatever is appropriate 

NOTE: Interesting enough Alexa Dev talked about deprecating AMAZON.LITERAL but there was a lot of people who told them to keep it.  This is using AMAZON.LITERAL but the other interesting part is when you define the SLOT the SCHEMA must have {whatever-you-want-here|TEXT}.  
